Python enforces implementation in child classes
    python will throw an error if child class doesn't implement abstract method.

class Cat(Animal):
    pass

c = Cat()  # ❌ ERROR

TypeError: Can't instantiate abstract class Cat with abstract method sound

class Cat(Animal):
